Program: Outlook
Title: Nip and tuck in Kabul
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yk1p6
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 5 Oct 2012
The plastic surgeon in Kabul who says demand for nose jobs, facelifts and breast enhancements is growing despite disapproval from some religious leaders. Also on Outlook,the terrible persecution faced by a transgender woman in Africa. Plus we hear from the 62 year old Chinese man who has devoted most of his life to the craft of violin making. Show less